canMove() - Method in class Ghost
if Ghost moves out of bounds or Pacman in PowerUp mode eats the Ghost, Ghosts can not move if there is a Pellet or Fruit, or Ghost eats Pacman, Ghost can move
canMove() - Method in class Pacman
The pacman can move only when the adjacent square is empty or if the adjacent square contains a bigPellet, smallPellet or fruit or ghost(only when the ghosts are blue, which is after the pacman eats a bigpellet)
Cherry - Class in <Unnamed>
Represents an edible Cherry in the Pacman game, that appears for bonus points for a limited time in level 1.
Cherry(int) - Constructor for class Cherry
